# HybridBonus — environment variable template
#
# No environment variables are required for local development today.
# Lovable injects its own values at runtime in the Lovable preview and published builds.
# Never commit real secret values to this file.
#
# If Lovable Cloud / Supabase is enabled later, the following slots are conventional.
# Leave the values empty here; set real values in your local .env (which is gitignored)
# or in the Lovable environment.

# SUPABASE_URL=
# SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
